Package net.sf.wubiq.proxies

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ProxyAdapter
    Proxy handler for server side classes.
    ProxyAdapterMaster
    Proxy for handling the communications of a server class in its master role.
    ProxyAdapterSlave
    Intercepts the objects' methods to ensure proper communication with remote parties.
    ProxyBase
    Defines the minimal implementation for proxied communication for clients, server in their master and slave roles.
    ProxyMasterBase
    The minimal implementation of a master communication proxy for clients and servers in their master role.
